title: Death Squad The Last Mission [Action, Eng, 2018]
description:
In our newest military shooter, the unfolds in Iraq. Take on the role of the American SEAL, whose detachment was left without reinforcements. You have one chance to complete the mission which is to destroy the enemies in any way, but whether you decide together with your squad to resist the enemy or to act alone depends on you. The main difference between this project and similar games is the realism of the events. You have the opportunity to choose your own way to survive in this world, which, naturally, is not ready to forgive your mistakes. Explore the huge map where the environment affects gameplay and decisions. There is a dynamic system of aiming with a slow-motion system and a quick change of weapons, as well as a realistic loss of soldiers. Also, you will be able to swerve to the sides for shooting from the shelter.

System:

ОС: Windows 7 +
CPU: 2 GHz
RAM: 512 mb
VRAM: 256 mb
HDD: 477 mb
